nodes.text: During the early years of the Galactic Empire, a station manager commanded Sel Zonn Station, an XQ2 Platform that orbited the planet Brentaal IV. At some point, the droid information broker Switch began operating out of Deep Storage Bay V14 in a restricted part of the station and Switch sent his Twi'lek majordomo to pay monthly bribes to the station manager, to keep the location of Switch's headquarters secret.
